    <item>
      <title>特朗普和哈里斯正在竞选，但过渡团队正在努力工作</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-02/trump-harris-on-the-trail-but-transition-teams-are-hard-at-work</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普和卡玛拉·哈里斯的团队都在悄悄筹备他们的候任政府，尽管两位候选人仍然专注于在周二极其接近的选举的最后几天赢得总统大选。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-02/trump-harris-on-the-trail-but-transition-teams-are-hard-at-work</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 02 Nov 2024 11:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国称超级富豪外国投资者威胁离开是虚张声势</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-02/uk-budget-labour-calls-bluff-of-ultra-rich-foreigners-with-tax-changes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[工党遭到了富人团体的猛烈抨击，他们希望避免在首份预算中受到严厉对待。本周，政府明确了选择：私募股权高管基本可以免于处罚，但非英国居民将多支付数十亿英镑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-02/uk-budget-labour-calls-bluff-of-ultra-rich-foreigners-with-tax-changes</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 02 Nov 2024 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>伊朗最高领袖称美国和以色列将遭到“严厉回应”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-02/iran-supreme-leader-says-crushing-response-awaits-us-israel</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伊朗最高领袖进一步升级言辞，警告称，在以色列一周前对伊朗发动导弹袭击后，伊朗将对包括美国在内的敌人进行“强力回击”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-02/iran-supreme-leader-says-crushing-response-awaits-us-israel</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 02 Nov 2024 09:30:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
